semaglutideincreasedtheserotonin(5-HT)andserotonintransporter(5-HTT)andglutamatergicreceptorsinthehippo-
campus.Atlast,semaglutidechangedthegutmicrobiotaprole(increasingBacterioidetes,Bacteroidesacidifaciens,and
Blautiacoccoides)anddecreasedleakygut,improvingthegut-brainaxis.Takentogether,semaglutidehasthepotential
